title: No Show Dems
description: Fellas welcome Washington Free Beacon journalist Matthew Foldi to discuss his report on Democrat office closures before discussing an endangered species of psychedelic toads. Monica De La Cruz and Mayra Flores join the progrum for an interview about their campaigns for Congress from Texas.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan, Comfortably Smug, John Ashbrook, Matthew Foldi, Monica De La Cruz, Mayra Flores)
